STATE
v.
Antoine Dwayne WELLS. No. 100P05. Supreme Court of North Carolina. January 26, 2006. William P. Hart, Special Deputy Attorney General, Peter S. Gilchrist, III, District Attorney, for State of NC.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 14th day of February 2005 by Defendant for Appropriate Relief:
